data.description: Discover the perfect blend of style and comfort in this 3 bedroom home with a 3 car garage and situated in convenient Wasson Place.  This residence boasts a timeless all brick exterior and is ready to welcome you.  Cozy up in the spacious living room with a gas fireplace. And create cherished memories in the formal dining room, perfect for special occasions.  the kitchen features hardwood flooring and newer stainless steel appliances where you can prepare a snack or a gourmet meal.  With the split bedroom  arrangement, there is privacy for any family member or guests. Outside, a patio area, trees and privacy fence make this space perfect for outdoor relaxation and entertaining.
